v 1.0.3
d wtttable: APA Word tables for Welch two-sample t tests
d
d wtttable creates APA-style Word tables for two independent-group
d Welch t tests across multiple outcomes, with FDR adjustment and
d absolute Hedges' g_av effect sizes. It can display compact Item01-style
d labels and create a separate Word mapping document for full item labels
d and block/subscale headings. The results() dataset retains signed effect
d sizes, standard errors, and signed confidence limits.
d
d Author: Hao Ma
d
